{"abstract": "Both cases highlight just how hard it is to convict those involved in complex corporate decisions where there is diffuse responsibility.", "web_url": "https://www.nytimes.com/2016/03/01/business/dealbook/deepwater-horizon-and-dewey-leboeuf-cases-share-challenges.html", "snippet": "Both cases highlight just how hard it is to convict those involved in complex corporate decisions where there is diffuse responsibility.", "lead_paragraph": "The explosion of the Deepwater Horizon drilling rig in the Gulf of Mexico in 2010 and the demise of venerable New York law firm Dewey & Leboeuf in 2012 could not be more different. One causing widespread pollution along with 11 deaths, while the other involved questionable accounting to keep the firm afloat as it struggled to deal with a changing marketplace.", "source": "The New York Times", "multimedia": [{"rank": 0, "subtype": "xlarge", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2016/03/01/business/db-whitecollar1/db-whitecollar1-articleLarge.jpg", "height": 450, "width": 600, "subType": "xlarge", "crop_name": "articleLarge", "legacy": {"xlarge": "images/2016/03/01/business/db-whitecollar1/db-whitecollar1-articleLarge.jpg", "xlargewidth": 600, "xlargeheight": 450}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "jumbo", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2016/03/01/business/db-whitecollar1/db-whitecollar1-jumbo.jpg", "height": 768, "width": 1024, "subType": "jumbo", "crop_name": "jumbo", "legacy": {}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "superJumbo", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2016/03/01/business/db-whitecollar1/db-whitecollar1-superJumbo.jpg", "height": 1537, "width": 2048, "subType": "superJumbo", "crop_name": "superJumbo", "legacy": {}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "thumbnail", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2016/03/01/business/db-whitecollar1/db-whitecollar1-thumbStandard.jpg", "height": 75, "width": 75, "subType": "thumbnail", "cr